<span id="freeTextContainer2498506062394102939">Highly recommend...especially if 1999 was a year of significance to you.<br/><br/>Re-reading it now, nearly 20 years later (as we are a people owned by our technology), it&apos;s a mind blower!<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText2498506062394102939" style="display:none">Highly recommend...especially if 1999 was a year of significance to you.<br /><br />Re-reading it now, nearly 20 years later (as we are a people owned by our technology), it's a mind blower!<br /><br /></span>
