<span id="freeTextContainer4171406514492820420">Barry wrote this book in 1999, so it a whole different social landscape of fear than we have now. However, one can see the parallels between our worlds and a somewhat belabored book could be summed up in a handful of points. Let me see if I can do this.<br/><br/>People begin to see the things that they fear. Perhaps, we are all hypochondriacs at some level.<br/><br/>I have laughed at myself at this weakness, but I think we all have it. When exposed enough to an idea (fear), we will believe it.<br/><br/>Trust but verify.<br/><br/>Sex s</span>
  <span id="freeText4171406514492820420" style="display:none">Barry wrote this book in 1999, so it a whole different social landscape of fear than we have now. However, one can see the parallels between our worlds and a somewhat belabored book could be summed up in a handful of points. Let me see if I can do this.<br /><br />People begin to see the things that they fear. Perhaps, we are all hypochondriacs at some level.<br /><br />I have laughed at myself at this weakness, but I think we all have it. When exposed enough to an idea (fear), we will believe it.<br /><br />Trust but verify.<br /><br />Sex sells but fear may sell even better.<br /><br />Finally, I know so much less than I thought I did after reading this book. We all really do.</span>
